{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2189450/extras/\u88fd\u4f5c\u5404\u5f0f\u624b\u6416\u98f2!__8_.png?t=1736191498\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2189450/extras/1t.png?t=1736191498\" /><br>In Boba Tea Shop Simulator, you get to :<br>     \u25cfMake various type of drinks, add different toppings and try your best to satisfy customers.<br>     \u25cfManage the time well and add the right amount of toppings.<br>     \u25cfThe quality of your drinks will affect your score and popularity of your shop.<br>     \u25cfMaking drinks can also be satisfying with the in-game audio and hilarious physics you can play around with.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2189450/extras/newGif1-ezgif.com-optimize.gif?t=1736191498\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2189450/extras/2t.png?t=1736191498\" /><br>Being a shop owner isn't easy, you have to :<br>     \u25cfRestock different types of supplies and consumables.<br>     \u25cfBoil tea and clean up the mess you made.<br>     \u25cfFinding your own pace on doing the errands is the key to a successful tea shop.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2189450/extras/newGif2-ezgif.com-optimize.gif?t=1736191498\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2189450/extras/3t.png?t=1736191498\" /><br>     \u25cfSpending on the decorations and furnitures for your tea shop can be a good idea, the customers prefer clean and stylized shops.<br>     \u25cfYou can place the items anywhere you want and create your one and only tea shop in town.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2189450/extras/newGif3-ezgif.com-optimize.gif?t=1736191498\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2189450/extras/4t.png?t=1736191498\" /><br>     \u25cfBy completing different tasks, you can unlock more type of tea and missions, doing tasks can also increase your shop's popularity.<br>     \u25cfMaking smart choices during tasks can also affect how well your shop is going to do in the future.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2189450/extras/PSOTERGIF-ezgif.com-optimize.gif?t=1736191498\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2189450/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1736191498","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2189450/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1736191498","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2189450/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1736191498","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2189450/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1736191498","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"demos":[{"appid":2346910,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2189450/extras/\u88fd\u4f5c\u5404\u5f0f\u624b\u6416\u98f2!__8_.png?t=1736191498\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2189450/extras/1t.png?t=1736191498\" /><br>In Boba Tea Shop Simulator, you get to :<br>     \u25cfMake various type of drinks, add different toppings and try your best to satisfy customers.<br>     \u25cfManage the time well and add the right amount of toppings.<br>     \u25cfThe quality of your drinks will affect your score and popularity of your shop.<br>     \u25cfMaking drinks can also be satisfying with the in-game audio and hi